  messages_:
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3e0c323bd2a15d844af5a11751a9250e, type: 2}
    direction: 1
    message: 'Well done! You just triggered a cutscene. '
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3e0c323bd2a15d844af5a11751a9250e, type: 2}
    direction: 1
    message: 'In the bottom left corner you will see grey square with some information.
      When you select a player that corresponding players health, portret and action
      points will be visible. On the bottom there is a bar that represents your health,
      when this bar is empty you have been defeated. '
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3e0c323bd2a15d844af5a11751a9250e, type: 2}
    direction: 1
    message: 'When you get close enough to an enemy you will enter a combat state.
      In this state you select a player and plan out his actions ahead of time by
      rightclicking on the tiles you wish to walk. By pressing 1 you will equip your
      sword and 2 will equip your rifle. '
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3e0c323bd2a15d844af5a11751a9250e, type: 2}
    direction: 1
    message: Every action you do like walking, shooting and hitting with your sword
      will cost an action point. You only have a set amount of action points per
      round. When the round is over the enemy will try to defeat you.
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3e0c323bd2a15d844af5a11751a9250e, type: 2}
    direction: 1
    message: Try walking to an enemy, selecting the player and defeat your enemy
      by equipping your rifle and shooting him! Keep your HP and Action Points in
      mind!
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3e0c323bd2a15d844af5a11751a9250e, type: 2}
    direction: 1
    message: In the game there is also a initiative system. [WIP Need HELP]
